  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nA typo error on an important command-line option line `--dry-run` can cause undesired behaviour. \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nRun this...\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ truffle migrate --reset --dry-runn\r\n> Warning: possible unsupported (undocumented in help) command line option(s): --dry-runn\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd it will migrate, when the user clearly doesn't want to.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nTruffle migrate should stop when unsupported command-line options to avoid undesired behaviour.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nIt migrates!\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: macOS 11.6.4\r\n* Ethereum client: Ganache UI 2.5.4\r\n* Truffle version: 5.4.32 (core: 5.4.32)\r\n* node version: 16.14.0\r\n* npm version:  8.5.2\r\n",
